ns%20for%20relief.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20comes%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20the%20department%20can%20move%20forward%20with%20firing%20nearly%201%2C400%20of%20its%20staffers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20higher%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-when-does-interest-restart-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudent-loan%20balances%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20lower%20college%20attendance%2C%20education%20groups%20have%20a%20list%20of%20concerns%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-eliminate-education-department-executive-order-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edismantle%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%20released%20a%20report%20on%20Thursday%20%E2%80%94%20exclusively%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20%E2%80%94%20compiling%20responses%20she%20received%20from%2011%20national%20organizations%20regarding%20the%20impact%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-school-choice-vouchers-education-policy-exeuctive-orders-anti-woke-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump's%20education%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20students%20and%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fate%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%20was%20among%20the%20groups'%20top%20concerns.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20recently%20ruled%20that%20the%20Department%20of%20Education's%20plan%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-dismantling-department-education-means-supreme-court-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elay%20off%20nearly%201%2C400%20of%20its%20employees%20can%20proceed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20office%20%E2%80%94%20which%20the%20report%20said%20administers%20over%20%24120%20billion%20in%20grants%20and%20student%20loans%20annually%20%E2%80%94%20would%20lose%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Council%20on%20Education%20told%20Warren%20that%20%26quot%3Bdelayed%20funding%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20instances%20of%20student%20financial%20aid%2C%20can%20result%20in%20the%20inability%20of%20students%20to%20enroll%20for%20classes%20and%20persist%20through%20to%20completion%20in%20a%20timely%20fashion%2C%20causing%20them%20to%20take%20on%20more%20student%20loan%20debt%20to%20complete%20their%20degrees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelays%20in%20receiving%20federal%20student%20aid%20could%20also%20lead%20some%20students%20to%20turn%20to%20private%20lenders%3B%20the%20NEA%20said%20that%20private%20student%20loans%20often%20have%20riskier%20terms%20and%20can%20lead%20to%20predatory%20lending.%20They%20might%20be%20the%20only%20route%20students%20have%20if%20they%20cannot%20receive%20federal%20student%20loans%20promptly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20report%20comes%20amid%20a%20summer%20of%20changes%20for%20student-loan%20borrowers%20and%20education%20overall.%20The%20administration%20announced%20in%20April%20that%20it%20was%20restarting%20collections%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-reinstating-penalties-default-student-loan-borrowers-treasury-offset-program-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edefaulted%20student%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20five-year%20pause.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-when-does-interest-restart-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInterest%20charges%20resumed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%208%20million%20borrowers'%20balances%20on%20August%201%20after%20a%20year%20on%20pause%2C%20and%20Trump's%20spending%20bill%2C%20which%20he%20signed%20into%20law%20on%20July%204%2C%20codified%20significant%20changes%20to%20the%20repayment%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20the%20bill%20included%20a%20%24200%2C000%20lifetime%20cap%20on%20borrowing%20for%20professional%20students%2C%20like%20those%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-spending-bill-student-loans-cap-graduate-school-doctor-lawyer-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseeking%20medical%20or%20law%20school%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Average%20tuition%20is%20higher%20than%20that%20cap%2C%20and%20education%20analysts%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%C2%A0the%20cap%20could%20either%20turn%20students%20to%20private%20lending%20or%20lead%20them%20to%20forgo%20their%20advanced%20degrees%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spending%20law%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-major-repayment-overhaul-big-beautiful-bill-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeliminated%20existing%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20include%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20and%20replaced%20them%20with%20two%20options%3A%20a%20standard%20repayment%20plan%20and%20a%20new%20Repayment%20Assistance%20Plan%2C%20which%20allows%20borrowers%20to%20make%20payments%20based%20on%20their%20income%20with%20forgiveness%20after%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20organizations%20said%20in%20the%20report%20that%20the%20new%20repayment%20plans%20could%20leave%20borrowers%20with%20higher%20monthly%20payments%2C%20and%20minimal%20staffing%20at%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20will%20exacerbate%20the%20challenges%20of%20attaining%20affordable%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20repayment%20changes%2C%20the%20report%20also%20highlighted%20Trump's%20intent%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-student-loans-moving-to-sba-away-from-education-department-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etransfer%20the%20facilitation%20of%20student%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20to%20another%20federal%20agency.%20While%20that%20hasn't%20yet%20happened%2C%20advocacy%20group%20Student%20Borrower%20Protection%20Center%20told%20Warren%20that%20moving%20%26quot%3Bthe%20student%20loan%20program%20at%20a%20time%20when%20borro