nch%20government%20are%20at%20an%20impasse%2C%20and%20further%20strikes%20are%20possible.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20you're%20traveling%20to%20Europe%20this%20summer%2C%20be%20aware%20that%20you%20could%20face%20delays%20or%20cancellations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStrikes%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrench-air-traffic-controllers-olympics-allowed-turn-up-hours-late-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFrench%20air%20traffic%20controllers%3C%2Fa%3E%20affected%20over%20a%20million%20people's%20travel%20plans%20this%20month%20%E2%80%94%20and%20may%20be%20set%20to%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiting%20understaffing%20and%20poor%20management%20from%20a%20government%20agency%2C%20France's%20second-largest%20ATC%20union%2C%20UNSA-ICNA%2C%20went%20on%20strike%20on%20July%203%20and%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20day%2C%20an%20average%20of%20around%203%2C700%20flights%20were%20delayed%20and%201%2C400%20were%20canceled%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20Eurocontrol%2C%20the%20central%20organisation%20for%20air%20traffic%20management%20on%20the%20continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20estimated%20that%20this%20cost%20airlines%20around%20120%20million%20euros%2C%20or%20%24140%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effects%20spread%20beyond%20France%2C%20given%20the%20international%20nature%20of%20aviation%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20many%20neighbors%20frequently%20fly%20over%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-do-if-your-flight-canceled-delayed-aviation-strikes-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EATC%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20France%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20impact%20a%20third%20of%20flights%20across%20the%20continent%2C%20showing%20the%20disproportionate%20impact%20that%20disruptions%20in%20one%20busy%20country%20can%20have%20on%20the%20European%20network%20as%20a%20whole%2C%26quot%3B%20Eurocontrol%20wrote%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20Spain%20was%20the%20worst%20affected%2C%20followed%20by%20France%20and%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22110eb621-ed68-409e-9729-f5ffe750c9fb%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20this%20mean%20if%20you%20have%20travel%20plans%20in%20Europe%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20unions%20haven't%20announced%20any%20further%20action%2C%20it's%20possible%20there%20may%20be%20more%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrance's%20transport%20minister%2C%20Philippe%20Tabarot%2C%20called%20the%20demands%20%26quot%3Bunacceptable%26quot%3B%20and%20expressed%20annoyance%20that%20strikes%20were%20targeted%20in%20the%20busy%20summer%20vacation%20travel%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUNSA-ICNA%20wants%20pay%20rises%20in%20line%20with%20inflation%20following%20a%202023%20agreement%2C%20more%20staffing%2C%20and%20better%20working%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-ceo-michael-oleary-another-shot-100-million-bonus-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERyanair%20CEO%20Michael%20O'Leary%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20last%20Friday%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20stopping%20French%20air%20traffic%20controllers%20from%20closing%20the%20EU%20skies%20again%20next%20week%20or%20the%20week%20after%20with%20more%20of%20these%20unjustified%20recreational%20strikes%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Irish%20budget%20airline%2C%20Europe's%20biggest%2C%20canceled%20170%20flights%20affecting%2030%2C000%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20all%20means%20you%20should%20be%20wary%20if%20you're%20flying%20to%20France%20this%20summer%2C%20or%20have%20another%20journey%20flying%20over%20the%20country%2C%20known%20as%20an%20overflight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20plan%20is%20to%20travel%20between%20two%20European%20countries%2C%20the%20continent%20at%20least%20has%20a%20strong%20rail%20network%20as%20an%20alternative.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurostar-plus-upgrade-review-worth-it-for-good-deal-2025-7%5C%22%20target%