20anymore.%20Meanwhile%2C%20changes%20passed%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-big-beautiful-bill-impacts-wallet-taxes-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBig%20Beautiful%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20an%20increase%20in%20visa%20fees%20and%20a%20funding%20cut%20for%20the%20organization%20that%20promotes%20tourism%20to%20the%20US%2C%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20further%20decline%20in%20international%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20without%20major%20events%20like%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20tourism%20is%20big%20business%20in%20the%20US.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-cuts-impact-summer-vacation-national-parks-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETravel%3C%2Fa%3E%20generated%20%241.3%20trillion%20in%20spending%20in%20the%20US%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20the%20US%20Travel%20Association%2C%20and%20supported%2015%20million%20jobs.%20It's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20US's%20largest%20service%20exports%2C%20drawing%20%24181%20billion%20in%20spending%20from%20international%20inbound%20travelers%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brazil's%20former%20soccer%20player%20Cafu%20places%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20trophy%20into%20a%20glass%20cabinet%20during%20a%20media%20preview%20at%20the%20new%20FIFA%20World%20Football%20Museum%20in%20Zurich%2C%20Switzerland%20February%2024%2C%202016.%20%20REUTERS%2FArnd%20Wiegmann%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5a2c571c5124c9c658f85fcd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22547%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFIFA%20World%20Cup%20trophy.%3Cp%3EThomson%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20industry%20has%20already%20taken%20a%20hit%20under%20Trump.%20Simon%20said%20international%20travel%20to%20the%20US%20was%20down%20more%20than%206%25%20year-to-date.%20Noting%20that%20foreign%20visitors%20typically%20book%20far%20in%20advance%2C%20she%20said%20the%20second%20half%20of%20the%20year%20and%20into%20next%20year%20look%20even%20worse%2C%20with%20some%20IITA%20members%20reporting%20booking%20declines%20as%20high%20as%2040%20to%2060%25%20in%20some%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20US%20is%20still%20a%20top%20destination%20for%20international%20travelers%2C%20its%20market%20share%20has%20already%20been%20shrinking%20due%20to%20other%20destinations%20growing%20faster%20in%20popularity%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US's%20loss%20is%20also%20another%20country's%20gain%2C%20and%20Simon%20said%20destinations%20in%20Europe%20and%20Asia%20are%20already%20winning%20over%20travelers%20who%20are%20choosing%20to%20skip%20the%20US.%20China%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20has%20been%20opening%20up%20visa-free%20entry%20to%20more%20countries%2C%20drawing%20more%20visitors%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f664858b-e2dd-464f-a927-f77155d31f39%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Big%20Beautiful%20Bill%20makes%20visiting%20the%20US%20more%20expensive%20for%20some%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EErik%20Hansen%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%2C%20government%20relations%2C%20at%20the%20US%20Travel%20Association%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20surveys%20consistently%20show%20there%20are%20two%20primary%20factors%20that%20deter%20foreign%20visitors%20to%20the%20US%3A%20first%2C%20cost%2C%20and%20second%2C%20whether%20the%20US%20is%20a%20welcoming%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20One%20Big%20Beautiful%20Bill%2C%20it%20set%20us%20back%20in%20both%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20Hansen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recently%20passed%20and%20signed%20spending%20bill%20adds%20to%20the%20cost%20barrier%20for%20foreign%20visitors.%20For%20travelers%20visiting%20from%20countries%20for%20which%20the%20US%20has%20waived%20visas%2C%20such%20as%20Australia%2C%20France%2C%20and%20South%20Korea%2C%20the%20fee%20for%20their%20travel%20authorization%2C%20or%20ESTA%2C%20was%20increased%20from%20%2421%20to%20%2440.%20But%20for%20travelers%20from%20countries%20that%20require%20tourist%20visas%2C%20like%20China%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20India%2C%20a%20Visa%20Integrity%20fee%20of%20%24250%20was%20introduced.%20That%20fee%20is%20on%20top%20of%20the%20existing%20%24185%20tourist%20visa%2C%20making%20the%20new%20cost%20%24435.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20a%20family%20of%20four%20would%20be%20spending%20an%20additional%20%241%2C000%20on%20fees%20before%20even%20entering%20the%20US.%20Hansen%20said%20that's%20%241%2C000%20that's%20not%20being%20spent%20at%20American%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spending%20bill%20also%20cut%20match%20funding%20to%20Brand%20USA%2C%20the%20marketing%20organization%20that%20promotes%20travel%20to%20the%20US%2C%20from%20%24100%20million%20to%20%2420%20million.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHansen%20said%20Brand%20USA%20is%20%26quot%3Bour%20megaphones%20for%20welcoming%20the%20world%20and%20encouraging%20people%20to%20come%20to%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20travel%20businesses%20and%20destinations%20also%20count%20on%20Brand%20USA%20to%20sell%20them%20to%20international%20markets%2C%20adding%20it's%20likely%20to%20be%20smaller%20and%20more%20rural%20destinations%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20represented%20by%20Republicans%20in%20Congress%2C%20to%20suffer%20the%20most%20from%20the%20funding%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228669%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Protesters%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68785bb2f748d8c055f5c376%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20controversial%20crackdown%20on%20immigration%20in%20the%20US%20has%20caused%20some%20concern%20among%20international%20visitors.%3Cp%3EHyoung%20Chang%2FThe%20Denver%20Post%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e35c4e17-fbd5-40c9-b7f1-c2d3c855daca%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20image%20and%20messaging%20issue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESimon%20and%20Hansen%20noted%20that%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20countries%20affected%20by%20the%20travel%20ban%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20has%20not%20officially%20changed%20the%20rules%20for%20tourists%20visiting%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20stories%20of%20immigration%20crackdowns%20and%20international%20travelers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-plan-for-ice-raids-workplace-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehaving%20run-ins%20with%20ICE%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20even%20being%20denied%20entry%20to%20the%20US%20on%20some%20occasions%2C%20have%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanadian-us-travel-boycott-april-car-plane-down-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einternational%20visitors%20feeling%20unwelcome%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Several%20countries%2C%20including%20Germany%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20and%20Portugal%2C%20have%20even%20issued%20warnings%20or%20advisories%20to%20their%20citizens%20about%20visiting%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20focus%20on%20illegal%20immigration%20has%20been%20misinterpreted%20by%20many%20people%20abroad%20as%20they%20don't%20want%20any%20foreign%20visitors%20here%2C%20but%20that's%20absolutely%20not%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20Hansen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20has%20established%20a%20World%20Cup%20task%20force%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20ensuring%20%26quot%3Ba%20successful%20hosting%20of%20world-class%20international%20events%20that%20reflect%20the%20values%2C%20security%2C%20and%20hospitality%20of%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHansen%20said%20he%20has%20also%20spoken%20to%20cabinet%20officials%20who%20said%20they%20share%20the%20goal%20of%20making%20the%20US%20the%20best%20destination%20for%20international%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20has%20been%20some%20less-than-friendly%20messaging%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20them%20to%20come%2C%20we%20want%20them%20to%20celebrate%2C%20we%20want%20them%20to%20watch%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20said%20during%20the%20task%20force's%20first%20meeting%20in%20May.%20%26quot%3BBut%20when%20the%20time%20is%20up%2C%20they'll%20have%20to%20go%20home.%20Otherwise%2C%20they'll%20have%20to%20talk%20to%20Secretary%20Noem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nod%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkristi-noem-wore-rolex-watch-to-salvadoran-prison-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHomeland%20Security%20Secretary%20Kristi%20Noem%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20faces%20of%20Trump's%20deportation%20efforts%2C%20could%20be%20interpreted%20as%20not%20very%20welcoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20that%20it's%20necessarily%20a%20totally%20negative%20message%2C%20it's%20just%20not%20the%20friendliest%2C%26quot%3B%20Simon%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20administration%20should%20focus%20on%20getting%20a%20welcoming%20message%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20pushing%20for%20a%20welcoming%20message%2C%20the%20US%20Travel%20Association%20is%20also%20appealing%20to%20the%20White%20House%20and%20Congress%20to%20restore%20Brand%20USA%20funding%20and%20cut%20the%20increased%20visa%20fees%2C%20Hansen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20making%20it%20more%20expensive%20to%20come%20to%20the%20US%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20make%20any%20sense%26quot%3B%20given%20the%20administration's%20stated%20goals%20of%20growing%20US%20exports%20and%20lessening%20trade%20deficits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20self-imposed%20tariff%20on%20one%20of%20our%20largest%20exports%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-policies-bbb-international-travel-us-