22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintermittent%20fasting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20the%20days%20I%20eat%2C%20I%20have%20a%20Pressed%20Greens%20juice%2C%20an%20avocado%2C%20or%20grilled%20cold%20fish%20with%20salad%2C%20and%20nonfat%20Greek%20yogurt%20with%20fruit%20and%20seeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20start%20with%20fat%20and%20protein%20over%20carbs%2C%20as%20this%20energizes%20me.%20Once%20a%20week%2C%20I%20do%20a%2024-hour%20fast%20to%20reset%20my%20metabolism.%20I%20also%20regularly%20do%20cleanses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217856142-a915-442f-b1a7-3d76cf9212f0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20drop%20my%20son%20off%20at%20school%20and%20head%20to%20the%20office%20by%208%3A30%20a.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20me%2030%20minutes%20to%20drive%20to%20the%20office.%20When%20I%20joined%20Pressed%2C%20the%20office%20had%20a%20flexible%20policy%20of%20two%20days%20a%20week.%20I'm%20a%20big%20believer%20in%20bringing%20people%20together%20for%20collaboration%2C%20so%20I'm%20in%20the%20office%20at%20least%20four%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I'm%20not%20in%20the%20office%2C%20I'm%20in%20the%20field%2C%20either%20looking%20at%20stores%20or%20competitors%20and%20learning%20what's%20happening%20in%20CPG%20or%20traveling%20to%20our%20manufacturing%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20spontaneous%20calls%20with%20anyone.%20My%20style%20is%20more%20structured%20and%20planned%2C%20and%20I%20have%20one-on-ones%20with%20folks%20reporting%20to%20me.%20I%20even%20plan%20time%20to%20not%20have%20anything%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221fac6252-4436-42f6-82d8-7076d4d9db4c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20probably%20don't%20take%20enough%20time%20for%20lunch%2C%20but%20I%20eat%20with%20our%20team%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20cater%20lunch%20for%20the%20Pressed%20team%2C%20and%20it's%20usually%20a%20plant-forward%2C%20healthy%20meal.%20It's%20an%20incentive%20and%20a%20perk%20of%20coming%20into%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20helpful%20to%20sit%20with%20folks%20from%20different%20departments%2C%20and%20it's%20efficient.%20I'll%20eat%20with%20the%20team%20when%20I%20can%2C%20a%20meal%20with%20high%20protein%2C%20some%20greens%2C%20a%20thoughtful%20carb%20intake%2C%20and%20no%20bread%20unless%20I'm%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20visit%20stores%2C%20it's%20usually%20planned%20weeks%20in%20advance%20with%20our%20operations%20leader%2C%20and%20we're%20not%20there%20to%20audit%20them.%20We%20meet%20with%20the%20regional%20operations%20and%20store%20management%20teams%20to%20analyze%20how%20good%20our%20marketing%20is%20and%20look%20at%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1acebda-2c14-4c20-a006-638fa8d05134%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20wife%20will%20say%20I%20leave%20the%20office%20too%20late%2C%20but%20I%20try%20to%20leave%20by%206%20p.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20get%20home%20between%206%3A30%20and%206%3A45%20p.m.%20and%20try%20to%20have%20dinner%20with%20the%20family%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20days%20I'm%20later.%20My%20wife%20cooks%2C%20but%20occasionally%2C%20we'll%20order%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20dinners%20center%20on%20protein%2C%20vegetables%2C%20and%20a%20sensible%20carb.%20We'll%20also%20go%20to%20Pressed%20stores%20sometimes.%20The%20kids%20like%20that%2C%20and%20it's%20fun%20to%20get%20their%20perspective.%20They%20have%20good%20insight%20into%20what's%20relevant%20for%20their%20age%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20believe%20in%20the%20separation%20of%20work%20and%20life.%20For%20me%2C%20it's%20about%20work-life%20integration%2C%20not%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-work-life-balance-advice-boss-lessons-job-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework-life%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%20evenings%2C%20I%20play%20tennis%20with%20my%20wife%20or%20daughter%2C%20followed%20by%20time%20in%20the%20sauna.%20On%20Fridays%2C%20I%20swim%20or%20surf%20with%20my%20son%20in%20the%20ocean.%20Fitness%20throu