dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20that%20pivot%2C%20Ring%20announced%20a%20partnership%20with%20Axon%20in%20April%20that%20effectively%20revives%20the%20video-request%20feature%20for%20police.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20exploring%20a%20new%20integration%20with%20Axon%20that%20would%20enable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fring-doorbells-live-video-security-camera-police-fusus-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elivestreaming%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Ring%20devices%20for%20those%20who%20consent%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivacy%20and%20civil%20liberties%20groups%20have%20criticized%20Ring's%20video-sharing%20capabilities%2C%20citing%20a%20lack%20of%20transparency%20and%20concerns%20about%20unethical%20use.%20In%202023%2C%20Amazon%20agreed%20to%20a%20%245.8%20million%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazons-ring-pay-millions-settle-ftc-privacy-complaint-lawsuit-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esettlement%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20over%20allegations%20of%20privacy%20violations.%20Amazon%20denied%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Ring%20employees%20told%20BI%20they%20remain%20uneasy%20about%20the%20partnership%20with%20Axon%2C%20which%20is%20famous%20for%20making%20Tasers%2C%20which%20are%20used%20by%20law%20enforcement%20to%20zap%20people%20with%20electric%20shocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20Ring%20employees%20said%20customers%20may%20not%20don't%20fully%20understand%20what%20they're%20opting%20into%2C%20and%20it's%20unclear%20how%20video%20footage%20will%20ultimately%20be%20used.%20Data%20security%20also%20remains%20a%20concern%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225977%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20Ring%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e4d70e02c24b61be2078497%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223980%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERing's%20smart%20doorbell%3Cp%3ERing%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESiminoff's%20influence%20is%20also%20showing%20up%20in%20Ring's%20product%20roadmap%20and%20internal%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20long-delayed%20home%20surveillance%20drone%2C%20originally%20unveiled%20in%202020%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20launch%20soon%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20plans.%20Siminoff%20has%20been%20testing%20the%20drone%20in%20the%20office%2C%20though%20it's%20likely%20to%20debut%20in%20limited%20quantities%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20Ring%20introduced%20a%20new%20text%20alert%20feature%20that%20provides%20real-time%20updates%20about%20activity%20captured%20by%20its%20devices.%20According%20to%20a%20recent%20internal%20email%2C%20Siminoff%20told%20employees%20the%20alerts%20would%20soon%20be%20refined%20to%20notify%20users%20only%20when%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20unusual%20happens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20vision%20has%20always%20been%20that%20Ring%20would%20help%20super%20power%20our%20neighborhoods%20for%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Siminoff%20wrote%20in%20an%20April%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f2f12bb4-bca3-47e7-8a85-7977fdde693e%5C%22%3E'Bigger%20impact'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESiminoff%2C%20who%20founded%20Ring%20in%202011%2C%20sold%20the%20company%20to%20Amazon%20in%202018%20for%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshark-tank-ring-jamie-siminoff-guest-shark-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%241%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20official%20title%20now%20is%20VP%20of%20product%2C%20but%20he%20signs%20off%20his%20emails%20as%20Ring's%20%26quot%3BChief%20Inventor%20and%20Founder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20practice%2C%20he%20oversees%20not%20only%20Ring%20but%20also%20Amazon's%20Blink%20security%20cameras%2C%20Key%20in-home%20delivery%20service%2C%20and%20the%20Sidewalk%20wireless%20network.%20Ring%20doesn't%20have%20a%20formal%20CEO%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Siminoff%20returned%2C%20some%20staffers%20were%20apprehensive%20about%20changes%20he%20might%20make.%20That%20concern%20was%20reinforced%20when%20he%20introduced%20a%20new%20travel%20policy%20in%20April%20requiring%20employees%20to%20email%20the%20company%20about%20the%20purpose%20of%20each%20business%20trip.%20He%20cited%20high%20travel%20costs%20and%20said%20the%20emails%20would%20serve%20as%20documentation%20when%20%26quot%3Bauditing%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20employees%20pushed%20back%2C%20Siminoff%20doubled%20down%20in%20a%20follow-up%20message%2C%20reaffirming%20the%20policy.%20That%20second%20time%2C%20he%20pointed%20to%20a%20recent%20Jassy%20annual%20shareholder%20letter%2C%20which%20emphasized%20building%20a%20culture%20that%20encourages%20employees%20to%20ask%20%26quot%3Bwhy%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20path%20to%20smarter%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20all%20keep%20doing%20this%2C%20I%20am%20certain%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20have%20such%20a%20bigger%20impact%20on%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Siminoff%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68199ed2a466d2b74ab51e58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmazon%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FBrendan%20McDermid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20return%2C%20Siminoff%20has%20also%20made%20changes%20to%20Ring's%20leadership%20and%20operations.%20In%20late%20April%2C%20Chief%20Product%20Officer%20Mike%20Harris%20and%20Chief%20Technology%20Officer%20Mike%20Balog%20both%20exited.%20In%20their%20place%2C%20Siminoff%20brought%20back%20longtime%20lieutenant%20Jason%20Mitura%20to%20lead%20the%20product%20and%20technology%20teams%20across%20Ring%2C%20Blink%2C%20and%20Sidewalk%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiminoff%20has%20also%20consolidated%20Rings%20office%20footprint%20for%20%26quot%3Bspeed%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Befficiency.%26quot%3B%20Ring's%20Santa%20Monica%20office%20is%20shutting%20down%2C%20while%20Amazon's%20Hawthorne%20and%20Amsterdam%20locations%20have%20become%20headquarters%20for%20the%20combined%20Ring%2C%20Blink%2C%20Key%2C%20and%20Sidewalk%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6ed5a4e-0842-4627-a096-d0cc8f7028a4%5C%22%3E'Double%20our%20output%20immediately'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInternally%2C%20Siminoff%20has%20scrapped%20Ring's%20monthly%20all-hands%20meetings%20and%20replaced%20them%20with%20a%20steady%20stream%20of%20companywide%20emails.%20Many%20of%20these%20messages%20focus%20on%20eliminating%20bureaucracy%20and%20encouraging%20creativity%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20he%20launched%20a%20dedicated%20inbox%20where%20employees%20could%20submit%20new%20ideas%20(something%20Jassy%20has%20also%20done%20since%20becoming%20CEO%20of%20Amazon).%20While%20praising%20some%20of%20the%20more%20unconventional%20submissions%2C%20Siminoff%20also%20urged%20employees%20to%20vet%20their%20ideas%20through%20AI%20tools%20first%20to%20avoid%20duplication%2C%20and%20to%20consider%20the%20resources%20required%20and%20messaging%20clarity%20before%20pitching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiminoff%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20AI%20will%20be%20central%20to%20Ring's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%2C%20every%20promotion%20will%20have%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20employee%20used%20AI%20to%20improve%20operational%20efficiency%20or%20customer%20experiences%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20email.%20They%20will%20also%20have%20to%20explain%20how%20they%20%26quot%3Baccomplished%20more%20with%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20email%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-June%2C%20Siminoff%20also%20encouraged%20employees%20to%20use%20AI%20at%20least%20once%20a%20day%20to%20improve%20productivity.%20The%20following%20day%2C%20he%20circulated%20a%20memo%20from%20Jassy%20that%20warned%20job%20cuts%20could%20result%20from%20AI-driven%20efficiencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20all%20lean%20in%20on%20AI%2C%20could%20we%20launch%2010%25%20or%2010%20times%20more%20shit%3F%26quot%3B%20Siminoff%20asked%20in%20a%20recent%20email.%20%26quot%3BMy%20guess%20is%20if%20we%20really%20all%20fully%20leaned%20in%20on%20AI%20and%20pushed%20ourselves%20hard%20to%20create%20constraints%20that%20only%20could%20be%20overcome%20with%20the%20use%20of%20AI%2C%20we%20could%20double%20our%20output%20immediately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20of%20Siminoff's%20communications%20focus%20on%20technology.%20In%20one%20instance%2C%20he%20addressed%20a%20cultural%20issue%3A%20the%20excessive%20use%20of%20acronyms%20in%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20acronyms%20often%20obscure%20meaning%20and%20slow%20down%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20best%20thing%20we%20can%20do%20is%20use%20data%20and%20clear%20language%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt%20allows%20for%20faster%20and%20more%20accurate%20decisions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aekim%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eekim%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%2C%20Telegram%2C%20or%20WhatsApp%20at%20650-942-3061.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-r