.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E31-year-old%20venture%20capitalist%20Sam%20Awrabi%20has%20raised%20%2410%20million%20to%20exclusively%20invest%20in%20AI%20startups%2C%20calling%20the%20technology%20%26quot%3Bthe%20dominant%20force%20of%20our%20lifetime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20advancements%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bbigger%20than%20both%20mobile%20and%20web%20combined%2C%26quot%3B%20Awrabi%20said%2C%20in%20part%20because%20%26quot%3Bthe%20average%20person's%20productivity%20will%20be%20increased%2050%25%20to%2075%25%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAwrabi's%20AI%20Fund%20I%20will%20operate%20within%20his%20VC%20firm%2C%20Banyan%20Ventures%2C%20named%20for%20the%20tree%20whose%20prop%20roots%20enable%20it%20to%20spread.%20The%20fund%20specializes%20in%20AI%20infrastructure%20and%20software%20startups%20that%20have%20had%20the%20technology%20at%20their%20core%20since%20inception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20infrastructure%20front%2C%20Awrabi%20said%20startups%20working%20to%20reduce%20AI%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-may-lose-ai-inference-market-groq-cerebras-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einference%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fequinix-is-installing-advanced-liquid-cooling-over-100-data-centers-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecooling%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20have%20a%20massive%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-price-4-trillion-market-cap-ai-chips-chatgpt-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20already%20worth%20%244%20trillion%2C%20and%20we're%20still%20in%20the%20early%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BImagine%20what%20the%20new%20winners%20across%20the%20AI-native%20infra%20stack%20could%20be%20worth%2030%20years%20from%20now%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20app%20front%2C%20Aw