tly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0d08742-1f06-4380-98fb-3b43840d2c87%5C%22%3EThe%20IDEs%20of%20July%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWindsurf's%20main%20product%20is%20an%20Integrated%20Development%20Environment%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0(IDE).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-memo-ai-winners-startups-vibe-coding-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIDEs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0are%20coding%20tools%20installed%20on%20developers'%20computers%20%E2%80%94%20a%20bit%20like%20PowerPoint%20for%20writing%20software.%20They%20have%3C%2Fspan%3E%20become%20the%20go-to%20interface%20between%20professional%20programmers%20and%20their%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Cognition%20CEO%20Scott%20Wu%20announced%20the%20Windsurf%20deal%20this%20week%2C%20he%20described%20the%20main%20assets%20he's%20getting%20%E2%80%94%20and%20put%20Windsurf's%20IDE%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list.%20He%20wrote%20that%20combining%20that%20product%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Brapid%20adoption%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20AI%20software%20engineering%20assistant%2C%20Devin%2C%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20unlock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWindsurf%20CEO%20Jeff%20Wang%20highlighted%20the%20same%20point%2C%20saying%20the%20combination%20of%20Congition's%20autonomous%20coding%20agents%20with%20Windsurf's%20IDE%20will%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Bbreakthrough%20developer%20experiences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f0c014e-e793-4739-981a-3412f78d4f3a%5C%22%3EUnique%2C%20granular%20data%20model%20fine-tuning%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIDEs%20are%20valuable%20in%20AI%20because%20they%20provide%20a%20massive%20stream%20of%20unique%2C%20granular%20data%20on%20how%20human%20developers%20write%2C%20fix%2C%20ship%2C%20and%20update%20software%20code%2C%20said%20Armando%20Solar-Lezama%2C%20a%20distinguished%20professor%20of%20computing%20at%20MIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20why%20you're%20seeing%20so%20much%20dealmaking%20activity%20around%20some%20of%20these%20startups%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%20in%20an%20interview%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20Tech%20and%20AI%20companies%20aim%20to%20make%20AI%20models%20really%20good%20at%20coding.%20Solar-Lezama%20said%20that%20one%20way%20to%20stand%20out%20is%20to%20use%20the%20data%20from%20IDEs%20in%20the%20post-training%20phase%20of%20AI%20model%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20high%20level%2C%20building%20AI%20models%20involves%20two%20main%20stages%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20is%20pretraining%2C%20where%20tech%20companies%20vacuum%20up%20all%20the%20data%20on%20the%20internet%20and%20use%20it%20in%20huge%20training%20runs%20so%20the%20models%20learn%20a%20general%20understanding%20of%20how%20the%20world%20works.%20Everyone%20has%20already%20stripmined%20the%20web%20for%20this%20information%2C%20so%20there's%20not%20much%20advantage%20to%20be%20gained%20here%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20anymore.%20It's%20table%20stakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20comes%20the%20second%20stage%2C%20known%20as%20post-training%2C%20that%20fine-tunes%20AI%20models%20and%20polishes%20away%20bad%20behavior%20while%20giving%20them%20their%20distinctive%20style.%20This%20is%20where%20things%20differ%20from%20company%20to%20company%2C%20and%20you%20get%20custom%2C%20proprietary%20approaches%2C%20Solar-Lezama%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20these%20companies%2C%20once%20they%20have%20exhausted%20all%20the%20data%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20there's%20no%20second%20internet%20to%20mine%20for%20data.%20They%20are%20all%20hunting%20for%20alternative%20data%20sources%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20big%20advantages%20of%20IDE%20companies%20like%20Cursor%20and%20Windsurf%20%E2%80%94%20they%20have%20access%20to%20a%20rich%20stream%20of%20data%20that%20some%20AI%20model%20providers%20don't%20get%20to%20see%20directly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20IDE%20provider%20like%20Windsurf%20%3Cspan%3Ecan%20see%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eevery%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0keystroke%20and%20every%20time%20programmers%20run%20their%20code%2C%20as%20well%20as%20how%20they%20run%20it%20and%20how%20they%20debug%20it%2C%20through%20the%20IDEs%20installed%20on%20developers'%20computers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20provides%20unique%20access%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20information%20about%20what%20people%20are%20doing%20with%20their%20code%2C%20versus%20just%20what%20they%20might%20enter%20into%20the%20prompt%20box%20of%20a%20more%C2%A0simple%20coding%20website%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20a%20lot%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20Solar-Lezama%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20AI%20companies%20often%20provide%20the%20underlying%20models%20that%20power%20IDE%20products.%20For%20instance%2C%20Anthropic%20models%20mostly%20power%20Windsurf's%20IDE.%20However%2C%20these%20AI%20labs%20may%20have%20access%20to%20less%20detailed%20coding%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIDEs%20have%20a%20level%20of%20granularity%20that's%20impossible%20to%20get%20any%20other%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Solar-Lezama%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40busienssinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabarr%40busienssinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwindsurf-google-cognition-acquisition-ai-coding-developer-data-ide-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752742801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22