ness%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOracle%20is%20eligible%20for%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrusoes-project-stargate-data-center-tax-break-in-abilene-texas-2025-4%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520developer%2520of%2520the%2520first%2Cthrough%2520a%2520public%2520records%2520request.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E85%25%20property%20tax%20abatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Abilene%20data%20center%2C%20thanks%20to%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20city's%20local%20economic%20development%20corporation.%20A%20lower%20property%20value%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20abatement%2C%20would%20shrink%20the%20software%20giant's%20tax%20bill%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20has%20previously%20reported%20on%20the%20vast%20disparity%20between%20Big%20Tech's%20eye-popping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-development-true-cost-environmental-impact-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20center%20investments%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20seemingly%20minimal%20economic%20benefit%20they%20bring%20to%20local%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Abilene%2C%20Stargate%20developer%20Crusoe%20has%20committed%20to%20spending%20up%20to%20%243.5%20billion%20to%20build%20the%20data%20center%20site%20in%20exchange%20for%20its%20property%20tax%20abatement.%20Crusoe%20has%20also%20committed%20to%20creating%20357%20new%20full-time%20jobs.%20As%20Crusoe's%20sub-lessee%20on%20the%20property%2C%20it's%20Oracle%20that%20ultimately%20benefits%20from%20the%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20often%20insist%20that%20tax%20breaks%20are%20crucial%20factors%20in%20choosing%20where%20to%20expand.%20Economic%20development%20officials%20say%20that%20any%20additional%20revenue%20to%20cities%20and%20towns%20is%20good%2C%20even%20if%20that%20revenue%20could%20have%20been%20higher%20without%20tax%20abatements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOracle%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOracle's%20executive%20chairman%20and%20CTO%2C%20Larry%20Ellison%2C%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20property%20tax%20appeals%20himself.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sfgate.com%2Frealestate%2Farticle%2F3-million-tax-cut-on-Larry-Ellison-s-estate-3290230.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2008%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20successfully%20lobbied%20San%20Mateo%20County%20to%20lower%20the%20value%20of%20his%20property%2C%20a%2023-acre%20site%20with%20an%208%2C000-square-foot%20residence%20inspired%20by%20the%20country%20estate%20of%20a%20Japanese%20emperor.%20The%20county%20awarded%20him%20a%20%243%20million%20tax%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20County%20officials%20weren't%20surprised%20that%20Oracle%20filed%20a%20protest.%20The%20money-saving%20maneuver%20is%20often%20used%2C%20even%20if%20the%20company%20is%20already%20receiving%20other%20tax%20breaks%20or%20incentives.%20Texas%20law%20also%20gives%20any%20property%20owner%20(or%20an%20eligible%20sub-lessee%2C%20like%20Oracle)%20the%20right%20to%20challenge%20an%20appraisal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20very%20large%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gary%20Earnest%2C%20Taylor%20County's%20chief%20appraiser.%20%26quot%3BBut%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20you%20approach%20value%20in%20the%20same%20manner%20as%20you%20would%20any%20large%20company%20%E2%80%94%20Costco%2C%20Sam's%2C%20Walmart%2C%20or%20any%20of%20those%20guys.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarnest's%20appraisal%20valued%20the%20Stargate%20site%20at%20about%20%24200%20million%20for%20the%202025%20tax%20year.%20He%20said%20it%20would%20be%20impossible%20to%20calculate%20what%20Oracle%20would%20pay%20in%20taxes%20at%20that%20valuation%20and%20with%20no%20abatement%2C%20because%20Texas%20property%20tax%20rates%20fluctuate%20from%20year%20to%20year%20and%20can%20be%20unpredictable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElijah%20Anderson%2C%20Taylor%20County's%20auditor%2C%20said%20that%20more%20than%20half%20the%20county's%20new%20property%20value%20this%20year%20came%20from%20Lanciu