1990s%2C%20Davinder%20Singh%20Mushkabad%20had%20his%20heart%20set%20on%20the%20United%20States.%20He%20was%20young%2C%20ambitious%2C%20and%2C%20like%20many%20in%20Punjab%20at%20the%20time%2C%20believed%20that%20a%20better%20life%20awaited%20abroad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20elder%20brother%20had%20already%20made%20it%20to%20the%20US%2C%20and%20Davinder%20was%20keen%20to%20follow%20his%20footsteps.%20With%20a%20university%20degree%20and%20a%20background%20in%20the%20Sikh%20Regiment%2C%20he%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20strong%20candidate.%20But%20fate%20had%20other%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F209087%2Fhow-to-apply-for-visa-usa-europe-travel-india-jov30%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evisa%20application%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20rejected.%20For%20many%2C%20this%20might%20have%20marked%20the%20end%20of%20ambition.%20But%20for%20Davinder%2C%20it%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20something%20far%20more%20grounded%3B%20quite%20literally.%20He%20returned%20to%20his%20village%20of%20Mushkabad%20near%20Samrala%20in%20Punjab%2C%20not%20to%20sulk%2C%20but%20to%20sow%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20began%20as%20a%20detour%20quickly%20became%20a%20mission.%20Over%20the%20next%20three%20decades%2C%20Davinder%20transformed%20a%20small%20farm%20into%20a%20thriving%20agricultural%20enterprise%2C%20one%20that%20not%20only%20sustained%20his%20own%20family%20but%20also%20empowered%20over%20230%20other%20farmers%20to%20take%20control%20of%20their%20land%2C%20their%20produce%2C%20and%20their%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20modest%20beginnings%20to%20a%20new%20direction%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavinder%E2%80%99s%20journey%20into%20agriculture%20was%20born%20out%20of%20necessity.%20In%201992%2C%20he%20began%20farming%20with%20just%20half%20an%20acre%20of%20chillies.%20The%20yield%20earned%20him%20Rs%2045%2C000%2C%20which%20was%20not%20a%20windfall%2C%20but%20enough%20to%20spark%20hope.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Davinder%20Singh%20Mushkabad's%20farm%20from%20a%20bird's%20eye%20view.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471124%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDavinder%20Singh%20Mushkabad%E2%80%99s%20farm%20from%20a%20bird%E2%80%99s%20eye%20view.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20wife%2C%20Baljit%20Kaur%2C%20took%20up%20dairy%20farming%20to%20supplement%20the%20family%20income.%20Together%2C%20they%20saved%20and%20slowly%20expanded%20operations%20to%20ten%20acres%2C%20adding%20tomatoes%20and%20other%20seasonal%20crops%20into%20the%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Davinder%E2%80%99s%20goals%20weren%E2%80%99t%20limited%20to%20daily%20sustenance.%20He%20was%20watching%2C%20learning%2C%20and%20experimenting.%20He%20paid%20attention%20to%20water%20use%2C%20invested%20in%20drip%20irrigation%2C%20and%20studied%20the%20market%20carefully.%20His%20approach%20to%20farming%20was%20never%20passive%3B%20it%20was%20strategic.%20Even%20before%20formal%20training%2C%20he%20believed%20in%20treating%20agriculture%20as%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20turning%20point.%20In%202007%2C%20Davinder%20travelled%20to%20Spain%20and%20Italy%20for%20training%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F470043%2Fabhishek-reddy-left-crore-job-himachal-farm-permaculture-manali%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotected%20cultivation.%3C%2Fa%3E%20What%20he%20saw%20there%20shifted%20his%20worldview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20were%20growing%20crops%20in%20extreme%20conditions%20with%20the%20help%20of%20polyhouses%20and%20working%20collectively%20through%20cooperatives.%20They%20bypassed%20middlemen%2C%20focused%20on%20quality%2C%20and%20earned%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20observed%20that%20the%20climatic%20conditions%20in%20Italy%20were%20not%20that%20favourable%20for%20agriculture%20as%20compared%20to%20India%2C%20still%2C%20they%20were%20achieving%20high%20productivity%20from%20their%20fields.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20were%20using%20POLY-HOUSE%20to%20give%20an%20ideal%20atmosphere%20to%20the%20crops%20for%20their%20growth%20and%20development.%20Seeing%20all%20this%20was%20very%20surprising%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Davinder%20told%20Apnikheti.com.%20That%20trip%20planted%20the%20seed%20for%20a%20new%20model%2C%20one%20he%20would%20soon%20bring%20to%20life%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInnovation%20that%20grew%20more%20than%20crops%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20his%20learnings%20abroad%2C%20Davinder%20set%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F1391%2Fbamboo-house-india-a-journey-towards-green-livelihoods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebamboo%20polyhouses%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20his%20farm%2C%20later%20upgrading%20them%20to%20steel%20structures.%20He%20began%20cultivating%20high-value%20crops%20like%20coloured%20capsicum%2C%20seedless%20cucumber%2C%20and%20exotic%20vegetables.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eour%20vegetables%209876835433%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSCfzs0Vah0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FSCfzs0Vah0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Davinder%20Singh%20Mushkabad%20(%40SinghMushkabad)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSinghMushkabad%2Fstatus%2F1471851633332031495%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2017%2C%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20kind%20of%20produce%20rarely%20seen%20in%20local%20mandis.%20With%20careful%20use%20of%20fertilisers%2C%20water%20conservation%2C%20and%20seasonal%20planning%2C%20his%20farm%E2%80%99s%20earnings%20multiplied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20traditional%20wheat%20or%20paddy%20farmer%20might%20make%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20Rs%2080%2C000%20per%20acre%20annually%2C%20Davinder%E2%80%99s%20polyhouse%20ventures%20started%20fetching%20Rs%208%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20per%20acre.%20The%20returns%20were%20staggering%2C%20but%20Davinder%20knew%20that%20true%20change%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20come%20if%20the%20model%20benefited%20only%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20he%20founded%20the%20Agro%20Help%20Aid%20Society%2C%20inviting%20farmers%20from%20nearby%20villages%20to%20join%20hands.%20Over%20230%20of%20them%20came%20together%20to%20form%20a%20cooperative%20under%20the%20brand%20Farmers%20Agri%20Mart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20pooled%20their%20resources%20to%20buy%20inputs%20in%20bulk%20and%20sold%20produce%20directly%20to%20markets%20in%20Chandigarh%20and%20Delhi%2C%20cutting%20out%20exploitative%20middlemen.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20small%20farmers%20had%20bargaining%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavinder%20recalls%20his%20early%20days%20in%20the%20mandi%2C%20sitting%20with%20a%20weighing%20scale%2C%20calculating%20rates%2C%20and%20talking%20to%20customers%20directly.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20selling%20vegetables%3B%20it%20was%20about%20reclaiming%20dignity%20in%20a%20profession%20that%20had%20long%20been%20seen%20as%20unrewarding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecognition%2C%20mentorship%2C%20and%20a%20Visa%20revisited%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Davinder%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20been%20recognised%20with%20numerous%20awards%2C%20including%20the%20Ujagar%20Singh%20Dhaliwal%20Award%20for%20crop%20diversification%20in%202008%20and%20the%20ICAR%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Award%20in%202009.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%E2%80%99s%20served%20on%20advisory%20boards%20at%20Punjab%20Agricultural%20University%20and%20the%20Indian%20Agricultural%20Research%20Institute.%20His%20farm%20has%20hosted%20delegations%2C%20students%2C%20and%20curious%20farmers%20from%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%E2%80%99s%20also%20represented%20India%20in%20Malaysia%2C%20Azerbaijan%2C%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20and%2C%20in%20a%20full-circle%20moment%2C%20the%20United%20States%20%E2%80%93%20this%20time%2C%20not%20as%20a%20hopeful%20migrant%20but%20as%20a%20successful%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F125477%2Fkisan-diwas-successful-farmers-lucrative-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagricultural%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20a%20quiet%20victory%2C%20not%20of%20leaving%20the%20country%2C%20but%20of%20proving%20that%20success%20can%20be%20built%20from%20home%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindi