ploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183717.619-1752239561-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468158%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERaman%20Siddhartha%20and%20Manju%20relocated%20from%20London%20to%20Dharamshala%20to%20build%20a%20sustainable%20homestay.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%2C%20as%20it%20stands%20today%2C%20began%20as%20a%20piece%20of%20difficult%20terrain.%20It%20was%20constructed%20on%20a%20patch%20of%20land%20in%20Thathri%2C%20off%20Khanyara%20Road%20in%20Dharamshala%2C%20bought%20in%202018%20by%20filmmaker%20Raman%20Siddhartha.%20The%20idea%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20never%20about%20just%20building%20a%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20lived%20in%20London%20for%2025%20years%2C%20but%20I%20was%20born%20in%20Himachal.%20My%20father%2C%20a%20bureaucrat%2C%20took%20me%20to%20remote%20villages%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20grew%20up%20seeing%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekachcha%20makaan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mud%20homes)%20that%20were%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20the%20land%20and%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raman%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20never%20left%20me.%20It%20stayed%20in%20my%20subconscious%20that%20if%20I%20ever%20returned%2C%20I%20would%20build%20a%20mud%20house.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReturning%20to%20India%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20creative%20partner%20Manju%20Narayan%20in%202016%2C%20the%20couple%20initially%20explored%20the%20region%20as%20filmmakers.%20But%20the%20growing%20clutter%20of%20concrete%20homes%2C%20even%20in%20remote%20Himalayan%20corners%2C%20deeply%20unsettled%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20was%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20%E2%80%98develop%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manju%20says.%20%E2%80%9CConcrete%20everywhere.%20It%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20losing%20the%20soul%20of%20the%20land.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20build%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F445301%2Fkrithika-venkatesh-mud-homes-architecture-sustainable%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentirely%20sustainable%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20eventually%2C%20a%20homestay%2C%20began%20as%20a%20personal%20project.%20But%20soon%2C%20the%20scale%20and%20significance%20of%20what%20they%20were%20creating%20outgrew%20that%20scope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDidi%20Contractor%E2%80%99s%20architecture%20of%20resistance%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20their%20vision%20to%20life%2C%20Raman%20and%20Manju%20reached%20out%20to%20Delia%20Kinzinger%2C%20the%20German-American%20architect%20better%20known%20in%20the%20region%20as%20Didi%20Contractor.%20Based%20in%20Dharamshala%2C%20Kinzinger%20had%20already%20spent%20decades%20building%20eco-sensitive%20homes%20that%20honoured%20local%20traditions%20and%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%2C%20by%20all%20accounts%2C%20uncompromising.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20refused%20to%20use%20AutoCAD%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raman%20says.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20sketch%20was%20hand-drawn.%20Every%20angle%20was%20measured%20by%20instinct%20and%20wisdom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20architect%20had%20her%20doubts%20initially.%20But%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20intention%2C%20sincerity%2C%20and%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20desire%20to%20reconnect%20to%20their%20roots%20eventually%20won%20her%20over.%20Her%20involvement%20changed%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20structures%20at%20Kosen%20Rufu%20were%20designed%20using%20mud%20bricks%20made%20from%20earth%20sourced%20locally%2C%20dried%20and%20shaped%20by%20hand.%20%E2%80%9CDrying%20them%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raman%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20mountain%20weather%20is%20unpredictable.%20Many%20bricks%20were%20washed%20away%20by%20sudden%20rain.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20long%20walk%20to%20sustainability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20setbacks%2C%20they%20never%20resorted%20to%20cement.%20The%20foundation%20used%20bamboo%2C%20walls%20were%20packed%20with%20stone%20and%20mud%2C%20and%20even%20the%20roofing%20slate%20was%20locally%20quarried.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386103%2Fsustainable-architecture-in-india-green-pavers-cseb-earth-blocks-orient-stranded-board%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENo%20industrial%20material%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20brought%20in.%20The%20design%20incorporated%2018-inch%20thick%20walls%2C%20natural%20insulation%20using%20pine%20needles%20and%20dust%2C%20and%20multi-layered%20mud%20coatings%20that%20mimicked%20the%20strength%20of%20concrete%20%E2%80%94%20without%20the%20environmental%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183452.889_11zon-1752239828.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20design%20incorporated%2018-inch%20thick%20walls%2C%20natural%20insulation%20using%20pine%20needles%20and%20dust.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183452.889_11zon-1752239828.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183452.889_11zon-1752239828-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183452.889_11zon-1752239828-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183452.889_11zon-1752239828-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183452.889_11zon-1752239828-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468163%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20design%20incorporated%2018-inch%20thick%20walls%2C%20natural%20insulation%20using%20pine%20needles%20and%20dust.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20for%20this%20homestay%20began%20in%202019%20and%20spanned%20nearly%20four%20years.%20With%20no%20road%20access%20at%20the%20time%2C%20every%20material%2C%20from%20bricks%20to%20bedding%2C%20had%20to%20be%20transported%20by%20mules.%20%E2%80%9CFriends%20and%20family%20called%20us%20mad%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raman%20laughs.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20said%20this%20was%20a%20foolish%20thing%20to%20do.%20But%20we%20were%20clear%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20disturb%20the%20land.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20path%20to%20the%20retreat%20remains%20intentionally%20non-motorable.%20Cars%20stop%20some%20distance%20away%3B%20the%20rest%20must%20be%20walked.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20Didi%20ma%E2%80%99am%E2%80%99s%20principle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20home%20should%20adapt%20to%20the%20land%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20a%20small%20road%20exists%2C%20thanks%20in%20part%20to%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20with%20local%20authorities.%20And%20the%20road%20is%20primarily%20not%20for%20tourists%2C%20but%20to%20help%20the%20villagers%20in%20nearby%20homes%20access%20emergency%20care%20more%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20hostility%20to%20harmony%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20not%20everyone%20in%20Thathri%20was%20convinced.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20filed%20complaints%20against%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manju%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20anyone%20would%20build%20a%20mud%20house%20willingly%3B%20it%20was%20seen%20as%20something%20the%20poor%20do%20out%20of%20necessity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20beam%2C%20every%20brick%20at%20Kosen%20Rufu%20Village%20Recluse%20holds%20a%20story%2C%20not%20just%20of%20resistance%20to%20mainstream%20tourism%2C%20but%20of%20radical%20care%20for%20the%20land.%20One%20person%20who%20oversaw%20this%20careful%20dance%20between%20terrain%20and%20technique%20was%20the%20chief%20architect%20Naresh%20Sharma%2C%20who%20worked%20closely%20with%20both%20the%20founders%20and%20Delia%20Kinzinger%20to%20bring%20the%20retreat%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22No%20industrial%20material%20was%20used%20during%20the%20building%20of%20this%20sustainable%20home%20stay.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468167%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENo%20industrial%20material%20was%20used%20during%20the%20building%20of%20this%20sustainable%20home%20stay.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20copy-paste%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naresh%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20mountains%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20force%20your%20ideas%20on%20the%20land.%20You%20have%20to%20read%20the%20slope%2C%20feel%20the%20weather%2C%20and%20understand%20how%20wind%20moves%20through%20the%20valley.%20Only%20then%20can%20you%20build%20something%20that%20lasts%2C%20not%20just%20physically%2C%20but%20spiritually%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20time%20and%20tea%20heal%20most%20things.%20As%20the%20couple%20integrated%20with%20village%20life%2C%20attending%20weddings%2C%20sharing%20meals%2C%20and%20participating%20in%20festivals%2C%20their%20intentions%20became%20clearer.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manju%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20locals%20are%20starting%20to%20see%20value%20in%20their%20traditional%20homes%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20perhaps%2C%20is%20the%20most%20lasting%20impact%20of%20Kosen%20Rufu%3B%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20welcome%20visitors%2C%20it%20encourages%20local%20preservation.%20The%20couple%20now%20advises%20villagers%20not%20to%20tear%20down%20their%20ancestral%20homes%20and%20is%20considering%20hosting%20community%20workshops%20on%20sustainable%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20stay%20that%20teaches%20you%20to%20slow%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20retreat%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20%E2%80%98Kosen%20Rufu%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20a%20Japanese%20phrase%20meaning%20%E2%80%98peace%20and%20happiness%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20Buddhist%20practice.%20True%20to%20its%20name%2C%20the%20homestay%20offers%20little%20by%20way%20of%20luxury%20as%20conventionally%20defined.%20There%20are%20no%20TVs%2C%20no%20air%20conditioning%2C%20and%20often%2C%20no%20mobile%20signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20guests%20find%20mud%20cottages%20warmed%20by%20the%20sun%2C%20the%20scent%20of%20pine%20wood%2C%20and%20views%20that%20stretch%20beyond%20the%20folds%20of%20the%20mountains.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20no%20scaffolding%20like%20you%E2%80%99d%20see%20in%20cities.%20Most%20of%20the%20work%20was%20done%20by%20local%20artisans%20using%20traditional%20tools.%20It%20was%20a%20collective%20memory%20%E2%80%94%20something%20modern%20design%20has%20almost%20forgotten%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naresh%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20come%20here%20and%20at%20first%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20unsettled%20by%20the%20quiet%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manju.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20by%20the%20end%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20leave.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T190116.163-1752241146.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20weekend%20getaway%20at%20Kosen%20Rufu%20will%20recharge%20your%20soul.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T190116.163-1752241146.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T190116.163-1752241146-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T190116.163-1752241146-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T190116.163-1752241146-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T190116.163-1752241146-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468217%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20weekend%20getaway%20at%20Kosen%20Rufu%20will%20rec